OL,3,CIsrael using 'water as weapon of war'
OL,4,Cas supply down 94%, Oxfam says
OL,6,FIsrael is "weaponising water" in Gaza
OL,7,Fafter data showed the amount available
OL,8,Fhas plummeted by 94% since the
OL,9,Foutbreak of the war, Oxfam said.
OL,11,FThe charity said in a report that the
OL,12,Faverage Gazan now had around 4.74
OL,13,Flitres of water per day available to
OL,14,Fthem - just under a third of the
OL,15,Frecommended minimum for survival in
OL,16,Femergencies.
OL,18,FThe amount is less than what is used
OL,19,Fin a single toilet flush.
