OL,3,CIsrael using 'water as weapon of war'
OL,4,Cas supply down 94%, Oxfam says
OL,6,FHalima Begum, Oxfam GB Chief
OL,7,FExecutive, said: "Tragically, this is
OL,8,Fyet more proof of the horrors being
OL,9,Finflicted on the people of Gaza by the
OL,10,FIsraeli Government, which is using
OL,11,Fstarvation and, as this report shows,
OL,12,Fthe systematic deprivation of water as
OL,13,Fa weapon of war.
OL,15,FShe added: "The impact on families in
OL,16,FGaza is unimaginable, from people
OL,17,Fbeing forced to drink polluted water
OL,18,Fto facing rivers of sewage in the
OL,19,Fstreets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
