OL,3,CIsrael using 'water as weapon of war'
OL,4,Cas supply down 94%, Oxfam says
OL,6,F"These appalling conditions are
OL,7,Fcausing significant risk of
OL,8,Fdehydration and creating a breeding
OL,9,Fground for the spread of disease,
OL,10,Fputting many more lives at risk."
OL,12,FMs Begum said this behaviour left
OL,13,Flittle doubt that "this represents a
OL,14,Fclear violation of international law"
OL,15,Fand called on the new government to do
OL,16,Fmore to achieve peace in Gaza.
OL,18,FOxfam's report found five water and
OL,19,Fsanitation infrastructure sites had
OL,20,Fbeen destroyed every three days since
OL,21,Fthe start of the war.
