OL,3,CIsrael using 'water as weapon of war'
OL,4,Cas supply down 94%, Oxfam says
OL,6,FThe charity also said Israel had
OL,7,Fdestroyed all of the wastewater
OL,8,Ftreatment plants and 70% of all sewage
OL,9,Fpumps.
OL,11,FThe report said Gaza City has lost
OL,12,Fnearly all its water production
OL,13,Fcapacity, with 88% of its water wells
OL,14,Fand 100% of its desalination plants
OL,15,Fdamaged or destroyed.
