OL,3,CIsrael using 'water as weapon of war'
OL,4,Cas supply down 94%, Oxfam says
OL,6,FThey said more than a quarter of
OL,7,FGaza's population had now fallen
OL,8,Fgravely ill from easily preventable
OL,9,Fdiseases commonly spread via the
OL,10,Fextreme lack of clean water and
OL,11,Fsanitation.
OL,13,FMore than 38,000 people have been
OL,14,Fkilled and more than 80% of Gaza's 2.3
OL,15,Fmillion population have been driven
OL,16,Ffrom their homes, with most now
OL,17,Fcrowded into squalid tent camps,
OL,18,Ffacing widespread hunger.
