OL,3,CIsrael using 'water as weapon of war'
OL,4,Cas supply down 94%, Oxfam says
OL,6,FMonther Shoblak, general manager of
OL,7,FThe Coastal Municipalities Water
OL,8,FUtility, which is responsible for
OL,9,Fwater and sanitation in Gaza and with
OL,10,Fwhom Oxfam works, said he and his
OL,11,Fcolleagues "have been living through a
OL,12,Fnightmare" since the war broke out.
OL,14,F"But we still feel it's our
OL,15,Fresponsibility and duty to ensure
OL,16,Feverybody in Gaza is getting their
OL,17,Fminimum right of clean drinking water.
