OL,6,FIn a meeting with Israeli Prime
OL,7,FMinister Benjamin Netanyahu, he called
OL,8,Ffor the immediate release of all
OL,9,Fhostages, an immediate ceasefire and
OL,10,F"the protection of civilians,
OL,11,Funfettered access to aid in Gaza, and
OL,12,Fa pathway towards a two-state
OL,13,Fsolution".
OL,15,FOxfam urged the new Labour government
OL,16,Fto go further in putting diplomatic
OL,17,Fpressure on Israel and by ending arms
OL,18,Fsales to the country.
